Related Buzz Resuts!

Got a GSA? Want to show Google Buzz Results in the feed? Who doesn't?!

While the GSA is powerful at delivering results from within your enterprise social connections are also important to some clients.

Google Buzz, the latest social medium from Google, allows us to create buzz around any topic we find on the internet, whether that be a website, news item or random comment.

Related Buzz Results gives you an easy plugin to your GSA that allows you to quickly add results from Google Buzz right in line with your GSA results.

Version 1 available now.

Works in Safari, Chrome, Firefox 
